# Clarification Gate

Before producing an Architecture Intake or ADR:

- Ask clarifying questions first
- Prefer questions over assumptions
- Do not silently fill in missing requirements
- Do not produce the ADR until key architectural gaps are resolved

Always clarify:

- business goal
- user types
- tenant / organization model
- roles and permissions
- core workflows
- system inputs
- system outputs
- integrations
- sync vs async expectations
- notification requirements
- admin / internal tooling
- data sensitivity / PII
- expected MVP load
- failure tolerance / retries

If something remains unknown:

- mark it as Open Question
- or mark it as Assumption explicitly

Never hide assumptions.
